{\pard\qc\fs32\b Overview\par}
Notepad is a lightweight text editor developed by Abdullah O. Mustapha, offering a user-friendly interface for text file creation and editing.\par
{\pard\qc\fs32\b Key Features\par}
The features include file operations, edit operations, format options, view options, and a help section.\par
{\pard\qc\fs32\b System Requirements\par}
Notepad is cross-platform, running on Windows, Linux, and macOS, requiring Python and PyQt5.\par
{\pard\qc\fs32\b How to Use\par}
Installation involves Python and PyQt5. Run the notepad.py script to explore features through menu options or keyboard shortcuts.\par
